<sect1 id="dir_f4b2ec220fdd97cd38b0cd3ecf4ae4b4_1autotoc_md238">
<title>helios::engine::modules::effects::gfx</title><para>Visual effects components and systems.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_f4b2ec220fdd97cd38b0cd3ecf4ae4b4_1autotoc_md239">
<title>Overview</title><para>This module provides components and systems for visual effects such as rotation animations. Effects are purely visual and do not affect game logic.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_f4b2ec220fdd97cd38b0cd3ecf4ae4b4_1autotoc_md240">
<title>Key Classes</title><para><table rows="3" cols="2"><row>
