</entry><entry thead="yes"><para>Purpose  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>SpinComponent</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Stores angular velocity and rotation axis for spinning  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>SpinSystem</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Applies spin rotation to entities each frame  </para>
</entry></row>
</table>
</para>
</sect1>
